    "pages": [
        {
            "text": "I like playing with my friend Chuma.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12871.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We are good friends. When either one of us is sent somewhere, we go together.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12872.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "One day, my grandmother sent me to the shop to buy salt and cooking oil. I went with Chuma.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12873.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "On the way, we saw our friends playing football.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12874.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12876.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "I said to Chuma, \"Let's ask if we can play with them. I like playing football very much.\"",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12877.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Chuma replied, \"Let us go to the shop first, then we can come to play.\"",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12878.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "But I replied, \"Let us play first! Grandmother will not allow us to return.\"",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12879.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We joined our friends to play. I was the goal keeper. The goal posts were made of two big stones.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12880.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "I worked hard to catch the ball. My friends were not able to score any goals.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12881.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We played until the field was full of sand.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12882.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Then we went to the shop. Grandmother's money was gone!\u00a0I started to cry. Chuma shouted, \"Stop crying. You wanted to play first.\"",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12883.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We returned home without salt or cooking oil. We were very dirty and worried.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12884.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Grandmother was annoyed when we got home. The first question she asked us was, \"Where were you all this time?\"",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12885.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We had to tell her the truth. She forgave us but warned, \"Never again go to play\u00a0without permission.\"",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12886.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We went to feed the ducks.  Later on, we cleaned ourselves.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/12887.png"
        },
        {
